long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Tab Saver is a powerful extension that helps you organize and save your open tabs for later use. With Tab Saver, you can create folders to categorize and store your tabs, making it easy to access them whenever you need.

 Save your tabs with just one click and give each folder a custom name. Open all saved tabs at once with a single click or open specific folders individually. 

Stay organized and boost your productivity with Tab Saver!
